esp32h20.8.0

Readable

Implementors

In esp32h2::generic

?

Trait esp32h2::generic::Readable

source · 
pub trait Readable: RegisterSpec { }
Expand description

Trait implemented by readable registers to enable the read method.

Registers marked with Writable can be also be modify’ed.
